 **Tuk-tuk ride**: $10-$20\\n    3. **Public transportation**: $1-$3\\n5. Attractions:\\n    1. **Temple entrance fees**: $5-$10\\n    2. **Museum entrance fees**: $10-$20\\n    3. **Guided tours**: $50-$100\\n\\nOverall, a budget-conscious traveler could expect to spend around $30-$50 per day, while a mid-range traveler could spend around $80-$120 per day. Luxury travelers could spend $200-$500 per day or more.\\n\\nFor a 7-day trip to Bangkok, here are some estimated total costs:\\n\\n1. **Budget**: $1,000-$1,500\\n2. **Mid-range**: $1,500-$2,500\\n3. **Luxury**: $3,000-$5,000\\n\\nKeep in mind that these are just estimates, and your actual costs may vary depending on your specific travel plans and preferences.\\nHuman: hello",{"lc":1,"type":"143","id":"144"},"llama-3.1-8b-instant","constructor",["145","146","147"],{"content":"148","additional_kwargs":"149","response_metadata":"150"},["145","146","151"],{"content":"152","tool_calls":"153","invalid_tool_calls":"154","additional_kwargs":"155","response_metadata":"156"},["145","146","147"],{"content":"157","additional_kwargs":"158","response_metadata":"159"},["145","146","151"],{"content":"160","tool_calls":"161","invalid_tool_calls":"162","additional_kwargs":"163","response_metadata":"164"},["145","146","147"],{"content":"148","additional_kwargs":"149","response_metadata":"150"},["145","146","151"],{"content":"152","tool_calls":"153","invalid_tool_calls":"154","additional_kwargs":"155","response_metadata":"156"},["145","146","147"],{"content":"157","additional_kwargs":"158","response_metadata":"159"},["145","146","151"],{"content":"160","tool_calls":"161","invalid_tool_calls":"162","additional_kwargs":"163","response_metadata":"164"},["145","146","147"],{"content":"94","additional_kwargs":"165","response_metadata":"166"},["145","146","151"],{"content":"106","tool_calls":"167","invalid_tool_calls":"168","additional_kwargs":"169","response_metadata":"170"},["171"],"secret",["172"],"langchain_core","messages","HumanMes